{"type":"answer","id":171291,"parentType":"question","parentId":18835,"uid":18467,"contents":"美国就有限制共产党员移民的法律<br>\n见<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/aug/16/communist-party-members-still-barred-us-citizenship-trump\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/aug/16/communist-party-members-still-barred-us-citizenship-trump</a><br>\n<blockquote><br>\nThe restriction stems from the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/laws/immigration-and-nationality-act\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1952 McCarran-Walter Act</a>&nbsp;(also known as the Immigration and Nationality Act) which collected and reorganized immigration law. It has been amended since its original passing, but&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/ilink/docView/SLB/HTML/SLB/0-0-0-1/0-0-0-untrusted fake 2049bbs Communist party, remains.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只是目前执行上有难度，中共和美国消息不互通，对于一般的党员美国很难甄别出来【类似于在中共党内有禁止移民（裸官）的条款，但依旧是满朝文武藏绿卡】\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n\n</a><div class=\"meta clearfix\"><a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/ilink/docView/SLB/HTML/SLB/0-0-0-1/0-0-0-untrusted fake 2049bbs Communist party, remains.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只是目前执行上有难度，中共和美国消息不互通，对于一般的党员美国很难甄别出来【类似于在中共党内有禁止移民（裸官）的条款，但依旧是满朝文武藏绿卡】\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text pull-right\">2020-02-19</span>\n\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">2</b>\n</a>\n\n\n<span class=\"operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" class=\"aw-add-comment\" data-id=\"171291\" data-type=\"answer\" data-comment-count=\"2\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 2</a>\n</span>\n\n<div class=\"more-operate\">\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-answer__item_id-171291\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollo